{
  "name": "gqlopcheck",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "description": "Performs additional checks on your GraphQL operations to ensure they conform to your rules, whilst allow-listing existing operations and their constituent parts (and allowing overrides on a per-field basis). Rules include max selection set depth, max list nesting, require pagination, limit self-referencing loops, etc. Add your own rules!",
